column5: Stop by the Muskies Canada booth at the Spring Fishing and Boat show (feb 18-21) and get your ticket for the 2011 Muskie Odyssey April 9th in St.Catharines! $15 in advance or $20 at the Door April 9th!   Come out and support Muskellunge Conservation and Research!
I'm not going to the Fishing Show this year Dax but hopefully I'll see you at the Odyssey in April.  Always a great day !!
